2.

Functionality.
* A way of buying and paying for books.
* Ability to download and use the bought books.
* A search and browse funtionality.

Application domain.
The application domain is Android phone users who are customers at Ebogreolen.dk

Conditions
The specification of android devices vary greatly and the application should run evenly on all devices.

Technology.
The system will be developed entirely in Java and will be run on Android smartphones with Android version 2.3 or higher.

Objects

Responsibility
Making the user able to browse, buy, read and listen to ebooks and audiobooks.
